_sText:
Speed run map I made for the holiday time. This map was a little rushed to get it done before Christmas, but it turned out alright.

There are two bonuses both of which are in the same room. The one on the bottom is a kz bonus for my friend sputnik. The bonus on top is just a simple strafe bonus.


There was a bug where the map would force sv_airaccelerate to 150 from my surf prefab. If you have this problem you can re-download it from the alternative link. If you don't have this problem then don't worry about it
